front.title: •Insertion Planning
front.gametext: If your scout is in battle at an exterior planet site, subtract 3 from opponent's total battle destiny. OR Target opponent's character aboard an open vehicle moving to your scout's site. Draw destiny. If destiny +2 > ability, target goes to Used Pile.
front.lore: The Rebellion employees every advantage it has over Imperial machines. A corps of well-trained scouts can elude detection in proper terrain.

combo: Insertion Planning + Rebel Strike Team / Garrison Destroyed
